name: SPANAKI x BOLO 2 - Limited Edition Bags
description:
BOLO is a graphic design magazine, designed, published and distributed by the Milan based designer Marco Nicotra.

In italian BOLO means “regurgitated food cud”, a disgusting thing that nobody wants to see. This is a good representation of combining different techniques. And that’s what BOLO is: Graphics, photography, illustration and typography from different artists, all mixed together in a way that different techniques are combined by a main theme obtaining a new and effective result. Supreme!

SPANAKI loves and supports all types of creative “reuse”, that’s why we couldn’t resist making some BOLO clutches!! So, we created a special limited edition of five SPANAKI clutches made of BOLO.
